{"tid":1205533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平看完香港遊行影片神情凝重　指示共軍「嚴陣以待」","createTime":"2019-06-11T19:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T20:54:30.000Z","uid":80516,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a2ec8c988e330da0edd15974394dccf3e2cec6","tid":1205533,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:54:47.000Z","msg":"編輯中心 / 綜合報導 - 2019-06-11 21:00:09<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1549205295-be9de853d00a228aaa3764703eee7ea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F1549205295-be9de853d00a228aaa3764703eee7ea6.jpg&h=184758c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲習近平。(圖 / 翻攝自新華社)<br />\n<br />\n香港的「反送中遊行」有百萬人上街抗議，反對港府通過《逃犯條例》。不僅國外媒體關注，連北京中南海也密切掌握。根據海外華文媒體《博訊網》 11 日引述消息人士獨家報導，國家主席習近平在聽取了中南海核心智囊和御用團隊的綜合評估後，認為香港有失控危險。同時，還命令共軍及駐港部隊嚴陣以待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1560241231-10aae195150ca575b203c5dec5c7d36b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F1560241231-10aae195150ca575b203c5dec5c7d36b.jpg&h=fcef063f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲香港 9 日的「反送中」大遊行，各國媒體都有大篇幅報導，但中國大陸的主要媒體卻幾乎沒有任何報導。（圖／翻攝自 Anthony Kwan Getty Images ）<br />\n<br />\n中南海知情人士指出，習近平和核心幕僚觀看了香港示威的片段後神情凝重，並且認為香港局勢會有失控的危險。該知情人士還披露，「南部戰區和駐港部隊已經嚴陣以待，全面應對香港可能出現的各種狀況」；報導指出「黨指揮隨時待命」，一直是中南海對付國內外重大突發事件的最高指令。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據外媒駐港記者報導，香港特區政府、中聯辦和駐港共軍也保持和中南海聯繫，接受指令。如香港情勢蔓延，習近平或許會召開中央常委會會議，包括國家副主席王岐山在內，黨政軍最高層也都將列席會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190611/3436518/?fbclid=IwAR3DAnaphWPOkAwlAKbQW1sfBPrTkgCBmEnWF2MJfmX_ohhus53EEzUI27E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190611%2F3436518%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3DAnaphWPOkAwlAKbQW1sfBPrTkgCBmEnWF2MJfmX_ohhus53EEzUI27E&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4f7b529f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190611/3436518/?fbclid=IwAR3DAnaphWPOkAwlAKbQW1sfBPrTkgCBmEnWF2MJfmX_ohhus53EEzUI27E</a><br />\n<br />\n大家，野餐小心，珍重。"},{"pid":"e91dd012e712ba48da79b2d56cb09fb6bd49fef1","tid":1205533,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔會喇，100萬人未見過咩"},{"pid":"1a69ad955b968f9e9bd2468cb74ea6e53cf54d0e","tid":1205533,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:48:25.000Z","msg":"你連戒嚴都唔撚敢呀<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2de9983e72830d4ac621e014c1346e9e818870","tid":1205533,"uid":40003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:54:30.000Z","msg":"Content Farm"}]}